Package: RcppBoostCompute
Type: Package
Title: Rcpp interface to boost::compute
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-06-15
Author: Marc A. Suchard
Maintainer: Marc A. Suchard <msuchard@ucla.edu>
Description: Provides access to boost::compute from within 
  the R environment; boost::compute is a C++ wrapper around OpenCL
  with basic algorithmic support.
License: Apache License 2.0 | file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: C++11
Depends: 
    Rcpp (>= 0.11.1),
    BH (>= 1.54.0),
    BoostCompiledLibraries (>= 1.54.0)
LinkingTo: Rcpp,
    BH,
    BoostCompiledLibraries
Suggests: testthat
